又係好笑，自己搞小圈子，又覺得自己最有料，根本同對面班防暴狗一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7d5e5336e3a70ada65c46ba5fc2dbf42361f29","tid":1400903,"uid":46832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"咁下步可以做咩？"},{"pid":"4e67941efa0b9649352c33e76cabcadccbb15eac","tid":1400903,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"前線手足拉一個少一個<br />\n如果而家做嘅係為咗消耗警犬<br />\n就hit and run"},{"pid":"29b33fcc2245ce17b5ae20e563f91f3dc1c9d406","tid":1400903,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"民意"},{"pid":"1d9060153ba990e9d6df52f5392dea64f0e2c0c5","tid":1400903,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef07e8ec45a4296ccf0daa036e7a756fe0357466","tid":1400903,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb2cc69e26672bff16b520686e18bb68c458fa6e","tid":1400903,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e7d5e5336e3a70ada65c46ba5fc2dbf42361f29","tid":1400903,"uid":46832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"咁下步可以做咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"如果而家做嘅係為咗消耗警犬<br />\n就hit and run<br />\n<br />\n游擊不留守"},{"pid":"f26e840d1c62adec489f9508201cb060ad795291","tid":1400903,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"如果而家做嘅係為咗消耗警犬<br />\n就hit and run<br />\n<br />\n游擊不留守"},{"pid":"b00b0b059bd026bce267cc0a12ea85bb691dac37","tid":1400903,"uid":258302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"如果而家做嘅係為咗消耗警犬<br />\n就hit and run<br />\n<br />\n游擊不留守"},{"pid":"edf3831